Code Style
==========
Code is formatted using clang-format. e.g. in vimrc:
  map <C-K> :py3f /usr/share/vim/addons/syntax/clang-format.py<cr>

Code is linted using closure (which has limited node support, but it works on individual files):
$ npm run lint

Tests
=====
$ npm test
 or
$ npm test test/specific_test_file.js

Debugging
=========
Add a 'debugger;' statement in your test of choice, then:
$ ./node_modules/.bin/electron-mocha --renderer --debug --interactive ./test/

